{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/dawn-theme-how-to-customize-badges-color-and-size","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1670,"date":"2022-05-09T03:42:31","date_gmt":"2022-05-09T03:42:31","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1670"},"modified":"2024-03-09T22:51:41","modified_gmt":"2024-03-09T22:51:41","slug":"dawn-theme-how-to-customize-badges-color-and-size","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/dawn-theme-how-to-customize-badges-color-and-size/","title":{"rendered":"How to customize badges color and text size [all free themes]"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Shopify | Customize badges color &amp; font size\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/AA2pSxfKSAo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>By default, the Dawn&#8217;s theme &#8220;sale&#8221; badges will always show up with a blue background, while the &#8220;sold out&#8221; badges are shown up with a black background and white text.<br><br>Although you&#8217;re able to customize the accent color of your theme and change them, the Dawn theme does not allow you to change these colors individually.<br><br>In this tutorial I&#8217;ll be showing you how you can quickly customize these badges&#8217; colors and size in a just a few lines of code. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-adding-the-code-to-the-theme\">Adding the code to the theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>From your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Find the <strong>snippets </strong>folder and click on &#8220;add a new snippet&#8221;.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Name it exactly:<br><br><strong>ezfy-badges-color</strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1031\" height=\"819\" class=\"wp-image-3745\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/a1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/a1.jpg 1031w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/a1-850x675.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/a1-768x610.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1031px) 100vw, 1031px\" /><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1443\" height=\"662\" class=\"wp-image-3747\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/a2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/a2.jpg 1443w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/a2-850x390.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/a2-1200x551.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/a2-768x352.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1443px) 100vw, 1443px\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Copy the code below, paste and save.<br><br>[gist]157e9ab00467e7d31102a03f633484a0[gist]<br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Find the file named exactly <strong>theme.liquid</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Inside this file, press CTRL + F (CMD + F on Mac) to trigger the search box and find this:<br><br><strong>&lt;/head</strong><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Paste the following code <strong>above</strong> the line you found:<br><br><strong>{% render &#8216;ezfy-badges-color&#8217; %}</strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1321\" height=\"846\" class=\"wp-image-3751\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste1.jpg 1321w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste1-850x544.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste1-1200x769.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste1-768x492.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1321px) 100vw, 1321px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Nice! We&#8217;re almost there.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-adding-the-code-to-the-customize-page\">Adding the code to the customize page</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Find the file named exactly:<br><br><strong>settings_schema.json</strong><br><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scroll all the way down and copy this code. Don&#8217;t paste anything just yet!<br><br>[gist]4f05db4ed8789510598345f9c63cabeb[gist]<br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Now, at the bottom of this file, paste the code <strong>after </strong>the <strong>} </strong>sign, as the image below indicates.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1159\" height=\"861\" class=\"wp-image-3753\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste2.jpg 1159w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste2-850x631.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste2-768x571.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1159px) 100vw, 1159px\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Now save and you should be ready to go! <br><br>If you see any errors, you pasted the code on the wrong line; please refresh the page and try again.<br></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-customizing-the-code\">Customizing the code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Click on the three dots on the upper left corner, click on customize theme.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1292\" height=\"831\" class=\"wp-image-3755\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste3.jpg 1292w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste3-850x547.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste3-1200x772.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste3-768x494.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1292px) 100vw, 1292px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>On the left panel, click on &#8220;theme settings&#8221; and scroll down until you find &#8220;Badge colors &amp; font size&#8221;<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1253\" height=\"755\" class=\"wp-image-3757\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste4.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste4.jpg 1253w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste4-850x512.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste4-1200x723.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/paste4-768x463.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1253px) 100vw, 1253px\" /></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some other tutorials you may be interested in. They work with &#8220;Dawn&#8221; plus all Shopify&#8217;s free themes (Craft, Refresh, Colorblock, Taste, Ride, Studio, Crave, Origin, Spotlight, Publisher &amp; Sense):<br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-product-page-slideshow-with-arrows-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Arrows &amp; vertical thumbnails for Dawn&#8217;s product pages<span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/w4LaQF8cp1akInO4Cp/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-how-to-fix-zoom-images-size-mobile-desktop?source=blog-dawn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Dawn lightbox: responsive images, slider and arrows <span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media4.giphy.com/media/aBmvXTlfvHiPMXtx4a/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps?source=blog-dawn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Improve your website&#8217;s safety: block right click, image copying and more</a></p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Change the color of the Dawn theme&#8217;s sale and sold out badges with just a few lines of code.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1671,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[655,626,657,435,776,773,663,649,652,646,660],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/dawn-badges-1-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/dawn-badges-1-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/dawn-badges-1-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"acf":[],"tag_names":["Colorblock Theme","Craft Theme","Crave Theme","Dawn Theme","origin theme","publisher theme","Refresh theme","Ride theme","Sense Theme","Studio Theme","Tast